description:
I'm responding to a video by Brittany Venti that was filled with nonsense. No dog violence in this one though. It also ends up in a place you might not expect, so try to stick with it.

A huge thanks to Bronwen Dickey's excellent book Pit Bull: The Battle over an American Icon for a nice portion of the information found in this video.

Follow me on Twitter if you like: https://twitter.com/JoseNotAJay
My Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/JoseOnYoutube

Sources

Venti's video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5_lfquOq39Y&feature=youtu.be

https://www.dogsbite.org/pdf/dog-attack-deaths-maimings-merritt-clifton-2013.pdf
https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm5226a1.htm
https://maultalk.wordpress.com/2010/09/27/science-whores/

https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26403955
https://www.theguardian.com/news/datablog/2013/mar/27/dog-bites-data
https://globalnews.ca/news/2527882/torontos-pit-bulls-are-almost-gone-so-why-are-there-more-dog-bites-than-ever/
